description: The i3 received a facelift in 2018 that also brought along a sportier trim - the i3s. Upgrades included blacked-out chrome parts, a lowered suspension, model-exclusive wheels and a boosted power output from the standard model's 125kW to 135kW. It's still not exactly quick, especially by today's standards - one guy tried lapped the Nurburgring with it and posted a time of 10 minutes and 8 seconds when the top-tier EVs are posting sub-8 minute lap times.
creator: Keanny
